    "pages": [
      {
        "title": "Welcome to your Coach Selection!",
        "description": "<div>We would like to invite you to help select your coach for this program. At Axialent, we have a rigorous selection and readiness process for all of our consultants, but we are also aware that personal fit and connection is important when being coached. For that reason, we want you to be a part of assessing who would be the best coach for you in this process. <br><br>We have a group of coaches for you to choose from, with the intention of offering diverse experiences, business backgrounds, and cultures. <br><br>All of them are certified in Conscious Business and Business Application Coaching, beyond many other specific trainings and certifications they have acquired internally and/or outside our organization (i.e. assessment tools, coaching models, and facilitation skills). You can read more about each one in their bios:</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><a href=\"https://axialent-my.sharepoint.com/:b:/p/belen_zurita/EYlOAeooYBtCpnpwUvJ5FmYB-v_Sti3wr2plqxoDx2ciGg?e=MHG753\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kat Niewiadomska</a></div>\n<div><a href=\"https://axialent-my.sharepoint.com/:b:/p/belen_zurita/EclilT-AI8VKlUfq4-ScJHMBU_XGt2yVqUZeFfy9yvuz5g?e=4327Hq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Declan Scott</a></div>\n<div><a href=\"https://axialent-my.sharepoint.com/:b:/p/belen_zurita/EdLI6nBuddpIgvLcLMvfjsoBd7e7QuNaA7-HSMJehQrofQ?e=5GYwCm&%3d&sdata=U2RlYUIwRTMyK2VqZmkyUzBQNmVkM3VDdG5TdFgzbEE5S1I0UE1tSWZkbz0%3d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Timothy Altaffer</a></div>\n<div><br>Please, review their bios and let us know who you would like to work with.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Please, don't hesitate to contact us if you have any questions.<br><br>All the best,</div>\n<div>The Axialent Team</div>",
